{"id": "cpos036", "name": "Audio_KaiStudio_702_12_24", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Sensei, he's in the inner room.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "Hehe, don't call me Sensei. I haven't seen you in so long. Seems like you've grown taller?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Muuu~ don't treat me like a child.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "...<i>*chuckles* ...*sigh*</i>... Hiding in such a filthy place like this, no wonder folks couldn't find you. Even a cockroach wouldn't want to enter a place like this.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Ahaha… NEKO was able to find him on the streets only because Aroma-chan helped out. Then I asked brother Kai to...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "I'm aware. I've already heard about the details from Miss Nora.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Umm... so what are you gonna do next? No matter how much you knock, he doesn't seem to respond at all...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "I came here to confirm a few things, then I'll leave immediately. First, let's make sure that he's not dead in there, shall we?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Eh, probably not...He ate everything NEKO brought him. Then he put the utensils in front of the door like this. It's like he's a total recluse...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "Door Knock"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Xenon, someone's here to see you…\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "Hey, would you please open the door? You know who I am, don't you?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "...Looks like he still hasn't recovered…\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Kick_Table", "Kicks Door"], "content": ""}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "!?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "EHHH!?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Good afternoon. It has been a while.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Is it just me, or is this déjà vu? You in dire straits looking like crap, and then I bust in like a valiant hero.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...What do you want?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Didn't you hear? I'm here to confirm a few things. Little kitten, can you give us some alone time?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Eh? Ah, okay… NEKO will go wash the dishes.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "There's...quite a lot of instruments here. An old storage room for an instrument shop? Fits your current situation quite well, don't you think?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Okay, enough with the chit-chat. We've already got our hands on some clues regarding the enemy and some important information. Thus, Miss Nora and I think it's time we head to the epicenter of this entire incident——Node 08.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Oh? You haven't heard about it? I've already touched base with them and the two sides have exchanged all the information we've obtained. You've been away from the team for quite some time now, so if you're still interested, I can catch you up to speed in no time.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Figure as much. The pain one feels from losing a loved one, it's not like I haven't had similar experiences either. How about we set such serious matters aside for now? You think you'd feel better?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "I think I'd feel much better if you got the hell out of here right now.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Haha, very funny. Don't forget, if it wasn't for the fact that you could offer us major assistance in this operation, there's no way I'd be willing to come to this dump.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Don't be like this. Relax. \n...<i>*sigh*</i>... What a hassle. You don't know how to pull yourself out of this, do you? Catch.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Wah!?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "That's quite a nice guitar, eh? Play a song with me, will you?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Huh? I am not in the mood right now…\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still_ConneR", "Music"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……!\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Recognize this song? I really like it. The last song included on Crystal PuNK's album.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Stop playing…\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "You've spent the majority of your life trying to save the people around you, yet you have no idea how to save yourself. Is there anything more pathetic than that? Pick up that guitar, the prelude's about to end. Play this tune with me and I'll leave once it's over. Then you can continue to enjoy your pitiful life in peace.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... If that'll get rid of you.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still_Guitar", "Guitar"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "This truly is a wonderful piece. You can hear the elegant and exquisite flow of emotions. If Miss Pauline could hear it once more, she'd definitely be moved, wouldn't she?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Look at you. Are you crying? There's no need to keep it in.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Shut up.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "You haven't cried at all since then? I bet every time something bad happens to you, you always keep it bottled up inside. If someone ever forgets that tears can heal, music is always there to remind them.\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "As we agreed upon, I'll be leaving. Wish you the best of luck, Mr. Jackson.\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... What exactly is the point of you coming here?\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Perhaps you should ask those tears that are streaming down your face why? You wanted revenge but exacted it on the wrong person. If you still have a little bit of motivation, we've already got information on the real culprit. You're welcome to join the team whenever you want, what do you say?\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\nNo.\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "This stuff, it's all pointless now.\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Is that so? If you believe that stopping a worldwide terrorist attack and disaster is pointless, then I won't force you.\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……!\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Interested now?\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\nNo. Get the hell out of here.\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "... What a shame. Okay then, see you again soon... Maybe.\n"}, {"id": 63, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "せんせー、Xenonはこの中。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "ははは、先生呼びは勘弁してくれたまえ。\nところで、しばらく見ないうちに背が伸びたんじゃないか？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "む！子ども扱いしないで！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "ははは。\nふむ、こんな汚い場所に身を隠していたのか。\n見つからないわけだ。\nこの様子では、ゴキブリでさえ近寄りたがらないだろうな。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "あはは……NEKOもAromaっちのおかげでやっと見つけたの。\nそれからKaiさんにお願いして……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "ふむ、詳細はNoraさんに聞いて知っている。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "じゃあ……これからどうするの？\nどんなにノックしても何の反応もないけど……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "私はここにいくつか確認に来ただけさ。\nすぐに帰る。\nまずは彼らがこの中で死んでいないか確認するのが先決だと思わないかね？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "いや、うーん、たぶん大丈夫……\nNEKOが持ってきたものはちゃんと食べてるみたいだし。\n食べ終わった後の食器もちゃんと外に出されてるし。\nまあ、言っちゃえば引きこもりだよね……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "ノック"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Xenon、お客さん……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "扉を開けてくれないかね？\n私が誰だかわかるだろう？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……まだダメみたい……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Kick_Table", "ドアを蹴る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "えええ！？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "久しぶりだな。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "ところで、この場面にデジャヴを感じないかね？\n落ち込んでいる君、そして颯爽と登場する私。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……何の用です。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "聞こえていただろう？確認したいことがある。\n子猫のお嬢さん、少し二人きりにしてくれないかね？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "え？あ、うん……\nNEKOお皿洗いしてくる……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "ここには……楽器がたくさんあるのだな。\n楽器屋の倉庫か？\n君にぴったりだ。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "無駄話はここまでにしておこう。\n敵の手掛かりと重要な情報を手にした。\nさあ、そろそろ行動を起こす時だ。\n行こうではないか、事件の中心地——Node08へ。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "おや？\n聞いていなかったのかね？\n彼らにはもう直接会っていてね、情報のやり取りも済ませてある。\n君も長く殻に閉じこもっていたようだし、興味があれば君にも共有しよう。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "まあ、そうだろう。\n愛しい人を失う苦しみは、私も経験したことがある。\nひとまずはあまり重い話は避けた方が君にはいいかな？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "あなたが出て行ってくれたほうがいいです。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "ははは、ユーモアが効いている。\nこれだけは覚えておいてくれたまえ。\n私がわざわざこのようなネズミの巣に赴いたのは、君の力が今後私たちの作戦に大いに貢献してくれるであろうと信じているからだ。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "肩の力を抜くんだ。\nふむ、なかなか面倒だな。\n君もどのようにこの状況から抜け出せばいいか分からない。そうだろう？\nならば……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "うわ！？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "良いギターだろう？私と合奏しよう。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……は？いや、そんな気分じゃ……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still_ConneR", "音楽"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "この曲は、君もよく知っているはずだ。\n私はけっこう気に入っていてね。\nCrystal PuNKのアルバムの最後の一曲だ。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……やめてくれ……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "君は、人生の半分以上を身の回りの人々を救うために費やしてきた。\nにもかかわらず、君は自分の救い方が分からないと来た。\nこんな悲しいことがあるかね？\n早くギターを構えないか。もう前奏が終わってしまうぞ。\nこれを弾き終わったら、私は失礼しよう。\n君は君でその愍然（びんぜん）たる人生を謳歌するといい。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……それであなたがここから消えてくれるなら。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still_Guitar", "ギター"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "実にいい曲だ。\n細かい感情の流れを感じる。\nMiss Paulineが聴いたら、彼女も感動するのではないか？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "おや、これはこれは……泣いているのか。\n気持ちを抑えられないのだな。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……うるさい。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "あれから、一度も涙を流さなかったのかね？\nいや、おそらく君はこれまで何があってもそれを心の内に秘めてきたのだろう。\nだが、人が泣き方を忘れてしまっても、音楽はそれを思い出させてくれる。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "では、約束通り私は去ろう。\nさらばだ、Mr. Jackson。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……結局、何をしに来たんだ。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "それは君の涙に聞いてみるといい。\n復讐を誓ったが、相手を間違えた。\nまだ君にその心が残っているのなら、私は真犯人の情報を掴んでいる……とだけ伝えておこう。\nいつでも君の帰りを歓迎する。どうだね？\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\nいや。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "そんなことに、もう意味はない。\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "そうかね？\n世界的規模の災難を阻止することに意味がないと言うのなら、私は何も言うまい。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "おや、興味が湧いてきたかな？\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\nいや、出て行ってくれ。\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……それは残念だ。\nいいだろう。\nまた会あおう、機会があれば、の話だが。\n"}, {"id": 63, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "老師，他在裡面的房間。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "呵呵，別叫我老師了。不過這麼久沒見，妳好像長高了？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "呣～別把人家當小孩子一樣。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "呵呵。\n唉，居然躲在這麼髒的地方，難怪沒有被找到。這種地方連蟑螂都不願意進來呢。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "啊哈哈……是靠 Aroma 醬幫忙 NEKO 才在街上找到他的，然後就請 Kai 哥……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "我知道，詳細我已經聽 Nora 小姐說過了。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "那……接下來你要怎麼做？不管怎麼敲門他好像都不會有反應……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "我是來這邊確認幾件事情，馬上就會離開。首先先確認他是不是已經死在裡面了吧？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "呃，應該沒有啦……NEKO 帶來的東西他都有好好吃完，然後就把餐具放回門口這樣。像個繭居族一樣……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "敲門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Xenon，有人來找你……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "喂，請開門。知道我是誰吧？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……他好像還是沒有平復過來……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Kick_Table", "踹門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "欸！？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "午安，好久不見。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "不覺得這場景似曾相似嗎？落魄不堪的你，跟颯爽登場的我。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……你來做什麼？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "你聽見了吧？我來確認一些事情。\n小貓咪，能給我們一點時間嗎？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "咦？啊、好……NEKO 去把餐具洗一洗。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "這邊……有蠻多樂器的呢，樂器行的舊倉庫？很適合你現在這副德性。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "廢話不多說了。我們已經掌握了敵人的線索跟一些重要的情報，所以 Nora 小姐和我覺得是時候前往事件的核心——Node 08 了。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "喔？你還沒聽說？我已經跟他們碰過頭，並且交換了雙方擁有的資訊。你脫隊也有段時間了，所以如果你還有興趣，我可以馬上跟你同步一下。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我想也是呢。失去了摯愛之人的痛楚，我也不是沒有體會過。不如我們先別聊那麼嚴肅的話題你會覺得好些嗎？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我覺得你現在馬上滾出去我會好些。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "哈哈，真幽默。別忘了，要不是因為你對於行動有極大的幫助，我可不願意來這種老鼠坑。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "別這樣，放輕鬆點。\n唉，真麻煩，你不知道怎麼走出這種狀態對吧？接著。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "哇！？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "那是把不錯的吉他吧？跟我合奏一曲。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……哈？我現在沒那個心情……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still_ConneR", "音樂"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "認得這首曲子吧？我很喜歡呢。收錄在 Crystal PuNK 專輯的最後一首。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……別再彈了……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "你花了大半輩子在試圖拯救身邊的人，卻不知道如何拯救你自己，還有什麼比這更可悲的嗎？快拿起吉他，前奏要結束了。\n合奏完這曲我就離開，你可以繼續好好享受你的悲情人生。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……如果這樣能把你趕走的話。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still_Guitar", "吉他彈奏"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "真是首好曲子，聽得出細膩的情感流動。Miss Pauline 能再聽到的話肯定也會很感動吧？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "瞧瞧你，你在哭嗎？用不著忍住的。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……閉嘴。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "從那之後你都沒有哭過嗎？不，一直以來你遭遇到的事情，我想你肯定全悶在心裡。如果忘記哭的方法，音樂總是能讓人回想起來。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "那麼像約定好的一樣，我該走了，祝你順心，Mr. Jackson。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……你到底是來幹嘛的？\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "問問你臉上那些淚水是為何而流吧？想復仇卻找錯了對象，如果你還有一點動機的話，我們已經掌握了真兇的情報，隨時歡迎你歸隊。如何？\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n不。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "做這些都沒意義了。\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "是嗎？如果你認為阻止一場世界級的恐怖攻擊與災難是沒有意義的，我也不勉強你。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "有點興趣了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n沒有，你滾吧。\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……那真是太遺憾了。好吧，再會，如果還有機會的話呢。\n"}, {"id": 63, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "선생님, 방 안에 있어요.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "하하하, 그렇게 부르실 필요 없습니다. 어쨌든 오랜만에 봤는데, 조금 키가 큰 것 같군요?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "치~ 자꾸 애 취급하지 말라구요.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "하하하.\n흠, 이런 더러운 곳에 은신하고 있었다니.\n찾을 수 없었던 것도 납득이 가는군요.\n이런 곳은 바퀴벌레조차 가까이하고 싶어 하지 않을 것 같은데.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "아하하......NEKO도 Aroma 짱 덕분에 찾을 수 있었어요.\n그리고 Kai 오빠한테 부탁해서.....\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "자세한 내용은 Nora 씨에게 들어서 알고 있습니다.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "그럼...이제 어떡하죠?\n계속 노크를 해도 아무런 반응이 없는데.....\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "저는 단지 여기에 몇 가지 확인하러 왔을 뿐입니다.\n곧 돌아가야 하죠.\n우선 이 안에서 죽어버린 건지 아닌지 확인부터 해야겠군요?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "서, 설마.... 그럴 리가....NEKO가 가져온 것도 잘 먹는 것 같았는데.\n다 먹은 후 그릇도 밖에 잘 놓아놨어요.\n말하다 보니 조금 히키코모리 같긴 하지만...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "노크"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Xenon, 누가 찾아왔어...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "문 좀 열어주시죠. 제가 누군지는 알고 계실 테고?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "...아직 정리가 안 된 것 같아요....\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Kick_Table", "문을 발로 찬다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "!?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "에에엥!?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "오랜만입니다.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "그런데, 이 장면 뭔가 어디서 본 것 같지 않습니까?\n침울한 그대, 그리고 힘차게 등장하는 제 모습이.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......무슨 용건이지?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "이미 다 듣고 계셨겠지요? 확인하고 싶은 것이 있습니다.\n고양이 아가씨, 단둘이서만 얘기하고 싶은데 괜찮을지?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "네? 아, 알았어요.....NEKO는 그럼 설거지하러....\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "여기에는... 악기가 참 많이 있군요.\n악기 가게 창고인가요?\n당신에게 안성맞춤인 곳이군요.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "쓸데없는 이야기는 여기까지만 해두죠.\n적의 단서와 중요한 정보를 얻었습니다.\n자, 이제 행동을 개시할 때입니다.\n가지 않겠습니까? 사건의 중심지, Node08로.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "응? \n못 들은 겁니까? 그들과는 이미 직접 만나도 봤고 정보도 주고받았습니다.\n당신도 꽤 오랜 시간 껍데기 안에 갇혀 있었던 것 같고... 흥미가 있다면 당신에게도 공유해 드리죠.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "음, 뭐 그럴 수도 있죠.\n사랑하는 사람을 잃는 괴로움은 저도 겪은 적이 있으니.\n일단 너무 무거운 이야기는 피하는 게 좋으려나?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "지금 당장 여기서 꺼져주는 게 제일 좋을 것 같은데?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "하하하! 꽤 웃겼습니다. 하지만 이것만큼은 알아주셨으면 하는군요. 제가 일부러 이런 곳까지 온 것은 당신의 능력이 앞으로 우리의 작전에 큰 기여를 해줄 것이라고 믿고 있기 때문이죠.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "어깨의 짐을 덜어 놓는 겁니다.\n흠, 조금 귀찮지만...\n당신도 어떻게 이 상황에서 벗어나야 할지 모르겠다, 그런 겁니까?\n그렇다면...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "으아앗!?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "꽤 쓸만한 기타 아닙니까? 저와 한 곡 해보시겠습니까?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......하? 지금 그럴 기분 아니다....\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still_ConneR", "음악"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "이 곡은 당신도 잘 아는 곡이죠.\n꽤 마음에 드는 곡입니다.\nCrystal PuNK 앨범의 마지막 곡...\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......멈 춰......\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "당신은 인생의 절반 이상을 주변 사람들을 구하기 위해 써왔습니다.\n그럼에도 불구하고, 자기 자신을 구하는 방법은 모르고 있죠.\n이런 비극이 또 있을까?\n빨리 기타를 준비할 수 없겠습니까? 이제 곧 전주가 끝날 겁니다.\n합주가 끝나면, 그땐 저도 제 갈 길을 가도록 하죠.\n당신은 당신대로 지금 모습처럼 살아가시든지.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": ".....해주지. 이것으로 네 녀석을 쫓아낼 수만 있다면.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still_Guitar", "기타 연주"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "정말 좋은 곡입니다. 세세한 감정의 흐름을 느낄 수 있죠.\nMiss Pauline이 들으면, 그녀도 감동하지 않을까요?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "이런 이런... 지금 울고 있는 겁니까?\n마음을 억누를 수 없었나 보군요.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......닥쳐.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "그 이후로 한 번도 눈물을 흘리지 못했던 겁니까?\n아니, 아마 당신은 지금까지 무슨 일이 있어도 그것을 마음속에 간직해 왔을 테죠.\n하지만 사람이 우는 법을 잊어버린다고 해도, 음악은 그것을 생각나게 해준답니다.\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "그럼, 약속대로 저는 제 갈 길 가도록 하죠.\n그럼 이만, Mr. Jackson.\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......대체 뭐 때문에 여기에 온 거지?\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "그건 당신이 흘린 눈물에게 물어보시죠.\n복수를 할 대상을 잘못 짚은 거 아닙니까? 그런데 저는 진범에 대한 정보를 쥐고 있습니다... 그리고 당신에게 아직 복수할 마음이 남아있다면.... 뭐, 여기까지만 하겠습니다.\n마음이 생기면 언제든지 돌아오셔도 좋습니다, 어떻습니까?\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n됐어.\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "이제 더 이상 무의미해.\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "그렇습니까? 세계적 규모의 재난을 막는 데 의미가 없다고 한다면, 뭐 저도 더 이상 할 말이 없습니다만.\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "조금 흥미가 생겼습니까?\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n아니, 이제 그만 꺼져.\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......정말 유감이로군요. 알겠습니다. 그럼 이만. 또 만날 수 있었으면 좋겠군요.\n"}, {"id": 63, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "老師，他在裡面的房間。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "呵呵，別叫我老師了。不過這麼久沒見，妳好像長高了？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "呣～別把人家當小孩子一樣。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "呵呵。\n唉，居然躲在這麼髒的地方，難怪沒有被找到。這種地方連蟑螂都不願意進來呢。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "啊哈哈……是靠 Aroma 醬幫忙 NEKO 才在街上找到他的，然後就請 Kai 哥……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "我知道，詳細我已經聽 Nora 小姐說過了。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "那……接下來你要怎麼做？不管怎麼敲門他好像都不會有反應……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "我是來這邊確認幾件事情，馬上就會離開。首先先確認他是不是已經死在裡面了吧？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "呃，應該沒有啦……NEKO 帶來的東西他都有好好吃完，然後就把餐具放回門口這樣。像個繭居族一樣……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "敲門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Xenon，有人來找你……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "喂，請開門。知道我是誰吧？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……他好像還是沒有平復過來……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Kick_Table", "踹門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "欸！？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "午安，好久不見。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "不覺得這場景似曾相似嗎？落魄不堪的你，跟颯爽登場的我。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……你來做什麼？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "你聽見了吧？我來確認一些事情。\n小貓咪，能給我們一點時間嗎？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "咦？啊、好……NEKO 去把餐具洗一洗。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "這邊……有蠻多樂器的呢，樂器行的舊倉庫？很適合你現在這副德性。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "廢話不多說了。我們已經掌握了敵人的線索跟一些重要的情報，所以 Nora 小姐和我覺得是時候前往事件的核心——Node 08 了。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "喔？你還沒聽說？我已經跟他們碰過頭，並且交換了雙方擁有的資訊。你脫隊也有段時間了，所以如果你還有興趣，我可以馬上跟你同步一下。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我想也是呢。失去了摯愛之人的痛楚，我也不是沒有體會過。不如我們先別聊那麼嚴肅的話題你會覺得好些嗎？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我覺得你現在馬上滾出去我會好些。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "哈哈，真幽默。別忘了，要不是因為你對於行動有極大的幫助，我可不願意來這種老鼠坑。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "別這樣，放輕鬆點。\n唉，真麻煩，你不知道怎麼走出這種狀態對吧？接著。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "哇！？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "那是把不錯的吉他吧？跟我合奏一曲。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……哈？我現在沒那個心情……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still_ConneR", "音樂"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "認得這首曲子吧？我很喜歡呢。收錄在 Crystal PuNK 專輯的最後一首。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……別再彈了……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "你花了大半輩子在試圖拯救身邊的人，卻不知道如何拯救你自己，還有什麼比這更可悲的嗎？快拿起吉他，前奏要結束了。\n合奏完這曲我就離開，你可以繼續好好享受你的悲情人生。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……如果這樣能把你趕走的話。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still_Guitar", "吉他彈奏"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "真是首好曲子，聽得出細膩的情感流動。Miss Pauline 能再聽到的話肯定也會很感動吧？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "瞧瞧你，你在哭嗎？用不著忍住的。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……閉嘴。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "從那之後你都沒有哭過嗎？不，一直以來你遭遇到的事情，我想你肯定全悶在心裡。如果忘記哭的方法，音樂總是能讓人回想起來。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "那麼像約定好的一樣，我該走了，祝你順心，Mr. Jackson。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……你到底是來幹嘛的？\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "問問你臉上那些淚水是為何而流吧？想復仇卻找錯了對象，如果你還有一點動機的話，我們已經掌握了真兇的情報，隨時歡迎你歸隊。如何？\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n不。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "做這些都沒意義了。\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "是嗎？如果你認為阻止一場世界級的恐怖攻擊與災難是沒有意義的，我也不勉強你。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "有點興趣了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n沒有，你滾吧。\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……那真是太遺憾了。好吧，再會，如果還有機會的話呢。\n"}, {"id": 63, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "老师，他在里面的房间。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "呵呵，别叫我老师了。不过这么久没见，妳好像长高了？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "呣～别把人家当小孩子一样。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "呵呵。\n唉，居然躲在这么脏的地方，难怪没有被找到。这种地方连蟑螂都不愿意进来呢。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "啊哈哈……是靠 Aroma 酱帮忙 NEKO 才在街上找到他的，然后就请 Kai 哥……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "我知道，详细我已经听 Nora 小姐说过了。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "那……接下来你要怎么做？不管怎么敲门他好像都不会有反应……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "我是来这边确认几件事情，马上就会离开。首先先确认他是不是已经死在里面了吧？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "呃，应该没有啦……NEKO 带来的东西他都有好好吃完，然后就把餐具放回门口这样。像个茧居族一样……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "敲门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Xenon，有人来找你……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["??????"], "content": "喂，请开门。知道我是谁吧？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……他好像还是没有平复过