versation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "那是把不错的吉他吧？跟我合奏一曲。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……哈？我现在没那个心情……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still_ConneR", "音乐"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "认得这首曲子吧？我很喜欢呢。收录在 Crystal PuNK 专辑的最后一首。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……别再弹了……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "你花了大半辈子在试图拯救身边的人，却不知道如何拯救你自己，还有什么比这更可悲的吗？快拿起吉他，前奏要结束了。\n合奏完这曲我就离开，你可以继续好好享受你的悲情人生。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……如果这样能把你赶走的话。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still_Guitar", "吉他弹奏"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "真是首好曲子，听得出细腻的情感流动。 Miss Pauline 能再听到的话肯定也会很感动吧？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "瞧瞧你，你在哭吗？用不着忍住的。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……闭嘴。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "从那之后你都没有哭过吗？不，一直以来你遭遇到的事情，我想你肯定全闷在心里。如果忘记哭的方法，音乐总是能让人回想起来。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "那么像约定好的一样，我该走了，祝你顺心，Mr. Jackson。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……你到底是来干嘛的？\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "问问你脸上那些泪水是为何而流吧？想复仇却找错了对象，如果你还有一点动机的话，我们已经掌握了真凶的情报，随时欢迎你归队。如何？\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n不。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": [